128
00:06:20,279 --> 00:06:20,800
Here,

129
00:06:20,920 --> 00:06:21,600
here,

130
00:06:21,680 --> 00:06:22,319
and here.

131
00:06:22,519 --> 00:06:24,000
The large mole on her arm.

132
00:06:24,980 --> 00:06:26,060
Mole on her arm?

133
00:06:34,139 --> 00:06:36,279
(Lin Xia's arms were flawless.)

134
00:06:36,920 --> 00:06:38,319
(There's no mole.)

135
00:06:43,980 --> 00:06:45,660
