145
00:07:06,120 --> 00:07:07,319
(were all my doing.)

146
00:07:08,639 --> 00:07:10,040
(But this body...)

147
00:07:16,680 --> 00:07:17,360
Mr. Ye?

148
00:07:18,000 --> 00:07:18,519
Mr. Ye,

149
00:07:18,920 --> 00:07:19,500
