163
00:07:50,480 --> 00:07:51,000
Fine.

164
00:07:52,379 --> 00:07:53,639
Contact me anytime

165
00:07:53,920 --> 00:07:54,759
when you're ready.

166
00:08:10,959 --> 00:08:11,639
Master,

167
00:08:12,120 --> 00:08:14,079
Ye Dong realized Lin Xia isn't Lin Xia.

168
00:08:15,920 --> 00:08:16,920
Watch them

169
00:08:17,360 --> 00:08:18,160
around the clock.

170
00:08:18,759 --> 00:08:19,439
This case

171
00:08:20,399 --> 00:08:21,139
will close soon.

172
00:08:21,720 --> 00:08:22,360
- Yes.
- Yes.

173
00:08:24,600 --> 00:08:25,800
What's going on?

174
00:08:26,079 --> 00:08:27,000
The face is Lin Xia's,

175
00:08:27,360 --> 00:08:28,439
but the body isn't.

176
00:08:29,160 --> 00:08:29,959
Impossible!

177
00:08:30,399 --> 00:08:31,120
Dong,

178
00:08:31,519 --> 00:08:33,399
maybe the body is Lin Xia's.

179
00:08:33,600 --> 00:08:34,799
Could you be mistaken?

180
00:08:35,620 --> 00:08:36,740
She was my wife.

181
00:08:37,399 --> 00:08:38,919
How could I forget her body?

182
00:08:39,840 --> 00:08:40,960
This is not Lin Xia!

183
00:08:41,320 --> 00:08:42,720
That's bizarre.

184
00:08:44,320 --> 00:08:45,200
Unless

185
00:08:45,360 --> 00:08:47,139
this body consumed Lin Xia's body,

186
00:08:47,480 --> 00:08:48,559
leaving only her face?

187
00:08:48,879 --> 00:08:50,679
Are we writing a horror novel?

188
00:08:58,960 --> 00:09:00,039
Bai Cha is Lin Xia.

189
00:09:02,440 --> 00:09:03,679
Bai Cha is Lin Xia?

190
00:09:05,120 --> 00:09:06,039
No way.

191
00:09:06,600 --> 00:09:08,019
If Bai Cha were Lin Xia,

192
00:09:08,399 --> 00:09:09,960
she'd have killed for revenge.

193
00:09:11,279 --> 00:09:12,399
But this body

194
00:09:12,919 --> 00:09:14,120
isn't Bai Cha's either.

195
00:09:15,159 --> 00:09:17,159
Lin Xia didn't swap faces with Bai Cha.

196
00:09:18,919 --> 00:09:21,179
We need verification to be certain.

197
00:09:34,039 --> 00:09:34,960
Why do you keep

198
00:09:35,360 --> 00:09:36,559
staring at me today?

199
00:09:39,240 --> 00:09:40,799
You look beautiful when working.

200
00:09:44,039 --> 00:09:45,519
I never imagined

201
00:09:46,220 --> 00:09:47,220
