215
00:10:27,919 --> 00:10:29,600
When we first met,

216
00:10:29,960 --> 00:10:31,039
I was

217
00:10:31,919 --> 00:10:33,440
in purple, not red.

218
00:10:35,820 --> 00:10:36,419
Right.

