223
00:10:48,840 --> 00:10:49,879
I've always

224
00:10:50,080 --> 00:10:51,759
wanted to see you in red,

225
00:10:52,279 --> 00:10:53,960
but you never fulfilled that wish.

226
00:10:54,600 --> 00:10:55,480
So now,

227
00:10:56,039 --> 00:10:57,399
will you grant me this once?

228
00:10:58,399 --> 00:10:59,639
After we marry,

229
00:11:00,120 --> 00:11:01,159
I'll give you

230
00:11:01,440 --> 00:11:02,559
whatever you want.

231
00:11:02,840 --> 00:11:03,240
No.

232
00:11:03,639 --> 00:11:04,559
I can't wait.

233
00:11:05,360 --> 00:11:05,960
Come with me.

234
00:11:06,840 --> 00:11:07,440
Where to?

235
00:11:11,480 --> 00:11:12,840
You'll see soon.

236
00:11:25,840 --> 00:11:27,500
