255
00:13:25,960 --> 00:13:27,039
But now

256
00:13:27,759 --> 00:13:29,200
I don't need love anymore.

257
00:13:40,559 --> 00:13:44,120
(Cheng Nuo replicated Bai Cha's marks)

258
00:13:46,320 --> 00:13:48,200
