268
00:14:19,080 --> 00:14:20,259
Pitifully,

269
00:14:20,559 --> 00:14:21,320
Ye Dong,

270
00:14:21,840 --> 00:14:23,240
without her approval,

271
00:14:23,879 --> 00:14:25,919
